# Generic single-database configuration for Alembic migrations.

This directory contains database migrations for the EASM Core application.

## How to create a migration

```bash
alembic revision -m "description of the change"
```

## How to run migrations

To upgrade to the latest version:
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

To downgrade one version:
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

For more information, see the [Alembic documentation](https://alembic.sqlalchemy.org).
